Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以第三令咒再次命之
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber 把圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅三次命令的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,到底能说看透了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,连更近在身边的手下的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明都没能看透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能全是对于不解人心的王的报应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那… 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我做了个恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅变成了酒杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在伊莉雅身体里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了整整七个好大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅快要胀破了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后听到了羽斯缇萨大人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,头上面开了个大大的黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 世界烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣看着那些哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 切嗣不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人不会害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人会为了伊莉雅努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的愿望他一定会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让伊莉雅再受怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为切嗣好努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,完成重要工作以后 马上就会回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 小 樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 樱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 樱 樱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,雁夜君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,葵姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 雁夜叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雁夜爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都因为你违抗爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,给人添麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把你从瓦砾下面挖出来可不轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伽美什 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那滩泥巴把本王吐了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看来天意让本王再次君临这个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,治理地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是说你得到肉身了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,居然期待那种东西是许愿神器而争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,本次的闹剧 真是直到最后都结果难料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我被击中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有… 心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我进行什么治疗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伽美什
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来确实是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你和本王由契约联系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我因为那滩泥巴得到肉身时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能也被什么不合常理的东西缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是说那个给了我生命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,消灭全部Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,赢得圣杯的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,绮礼啊 好好观赏这个结局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果圣杯真的会理解胜者的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,言峰绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个景色才是你想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多么邪恶 多么鬼畜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这种破灭 叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的愉悦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这种扭曲 污物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏是出自言峰璃正的种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么 难道我父亲让狗怀孕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,满足了吗 绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 对于只是上下求索的人生 我终于得到了解答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 省略解开问题的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一下扔过来答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这要让人怎么信服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,导出此等怪异解答的方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定作为明快之理存在于某处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,必须存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,必须疑问 必须寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,费上这条生命 我必须要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,理解之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让人不厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,连神都会问倒的你的求道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,由我吉尔伽美什来见证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世上全部的恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,终将再次到达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而下次一定要见证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其存在证明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫… 切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然接受挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,眼中含着泪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为找到了生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而发自心底喜悦的男人的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他是如此的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像获救的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而是那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着 还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至让直面死亡的自己感到羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,男人像是在感谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说道 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,能找到太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能救到一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\bord0\shad0\blur1}Fate/Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在冬木市新都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,阿列克塞先生应该平安到达英国了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨从希思罗空港来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是考虑下时差啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 有来电话吗 我都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这才是那个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 爷爷 奶奶 我有件事商量 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么郑重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想暂时休学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当然也要和多伦多的父亲商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,比起在学校学习 我想把时间用在其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说讨厌学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只是先前对于学习以外的事情没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢… 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 听到了吗古兰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,韦伯突然说出了像阿列克塞先生的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,总之有很多要准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说需要盘缠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想要先开始打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然后啊 现在开始才是正题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,直到有个着落为止 我都可以在这里叨扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,又能和韦伯在一起了 真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 今天要庆祝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要怎样才能留下这么多痕迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其实希望你能带我一起走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还完全不像样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,结果根本没开封嘛 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,初次购买特典
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,附赠原创T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真有人会想要这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吾知吾主永生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}I know that my Redeemer lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一日会伫立于大地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}and that in the end he will stand upon the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}And after my skin has been destroyed, yet in my flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吾之皮肤被破坏 于吾之肉间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}I will see God
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吾将见到上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}I myself will see him with my own eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,吾将亲眼目睹之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}I, and not another
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,吾 非他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}How my heart yearns within me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吾心何等向往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\an8}Amen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,作为新家督的初次亮相 做得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,令尊也会为你骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,刻印应该还没完全适应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,时臣老师的安排着实完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂积累下来的魔导会毫无遗漏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,凛 被你继承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要把令堂带来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来和父亲大人最后告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 呃… 凛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是谁的葬礼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 父亲大人死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点把时臣的丧服拿出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 凛 帮樱换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明我也必须准备的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀亲爱的 你的领带歪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是凛和樱自豪的父亲大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要暂时离开日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,关于今后的事情有什么不安的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何要拜托你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下次见面是半年后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候也会执行第二次刻印移植
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一定注意健康管理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来你就是名副其实的远坂家家督了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这个日子 我想赠你一件东西庆祝新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,AZOTH剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,过去吾师认可我的魔术修行成果时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,收到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今后这个就由你来持有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是… 父亲大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,回到了这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯… 洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法舍弃对格尼薇儿的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法原谅这样的自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是亚瑟王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,您没有问罪于我 也没有要我补偿…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在我们面前保持正确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我希望由您亲手制裁我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能被您自身的怒火所制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能就不会因为追求补偿而堕入狂暴之道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我能肯定的只有这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亚瑟王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一定把圣杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,您才是最棒的王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,您的所有臣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,应当成为王的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,之后 我多次造访了爱因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于没能带回圣杯的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,尤布斯塔库哈依德拒绝打开森林的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再也没能见到伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅之后 从我的人生中被夺去的人 一个也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是应该只有失去的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家从相会的那天起就一成不变的陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我将那天救了的少年士郎收为养子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要睡觉就去被窝里睡哦 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊… 不 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经憧憬正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经憧憬 就是说已经放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄是有时限的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,长成大人后 想自称英雄会越来越困难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事 如果早点发觉到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 好美的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我来替你做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷是大人 已经没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,凯利你啊 想成为什么样的大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想成为正义的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:45.14,kasic,,0,0,0,,奇迹想必还能再度发生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:51.42,kasic,,0,0,0,,以温柔的声音描绘扭曲的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:54.55,kasic,,0,0,0,,若选择了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:23:02.32,kasic,,0,0,0,,得以找寻仅属两人的欢愉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.07,kasic,,0,0,0,,哪怕冰焰万般灼体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:10.28,kasic,,0,0,0,,亦受之若饴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:19.66,kasic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2810)}只要身边有你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:21.17,kasic,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(0,1420)}愿将这一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:26.13,kasic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}归于清澈的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.55,kasic,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(0,1960)}水中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:32.51,kasic,,0,0,0,,仅有悲哀无法抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:41.89,kasic,,0,0,0,,此等人心至理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:48.19,kasic,,0,0,0,,亦由此手撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:56.87,kasic,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(0,5000)}吾等尽归于零
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:56.58,kasic,,0,0,0,,皎洁的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:59.75,kasic,,0,0,0,,只是静静地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:04.29,kasic,,0,0,0,,腐朽于起始之地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:09.13,kasic,,0,0,0,,憧憬渐渐关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:12.26,kasic,,0,0,0,,仍向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:14.89,kasic,,0,0,0,,于黑暗间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:18.10,kasic,,0,0,0,,与君共渡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:21.64,kasic,,0,0,0,,岁月点点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.27,0:24:31.61,kasic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2610)}温柔的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:45.13,kasij,,0,0,0,,あと一度だけ奇跡は起こるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:51.43,kasij,,0,0,0,,優しい声で描く歪んだ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.56,kasij,,0,0,0,,君を選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:23:02.31,kasij,,0,0,0,,たった二人の歓びを探せたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:07.07,kasij,,0,0,0,,どんな冷たい焔に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.28,kasij,,0,0,0,,身を焼かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:19.68,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2810)}微笑みの近く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:21.16,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(0,1420)}この世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:26.13,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}澄んだ水の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:28.57,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(0,1960)}還したい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:32.52,kasij,,0,0,0,,哀しみだけ消せはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:41.88,kasij,,0,0,0,,そんな人の心の理さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:48.18,kasij,,0,0,0,,この手で切り裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:56.88,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(0,5000)}down to zero we go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:56.59,kasij,,0,0,0,,奇麗な月の光は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:59.75,kasij,,0,0,0,,ただ静かに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:04.29,kasij,,0,0,0,,始まりへ朽ちて行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:09.15,kasij,,0,0,0,,閉ざされた憧れは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:12.28,kasij,,0,0,0,,まだ遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:14.90,kasij,,0,0,0,,闇の中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:18.12,kasij,,0,0,0,,君と生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:21.65,kasij,,0,0,0,,日々の全て
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:31.63,kasij,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2610)}優しい歌
